# Frontend build context (Dockerfile does `COPY . .`). Keeps secrets and local
# state out of the image and stops the local node_modules/.next from clobbering
# the freshly-installed ones. Review #2.

# --- Secrets: NEVER send to the build context (incl. .env.local) ---
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# --- Deps & build output (reinstalled/rebuilt in-image) ---
node_modules
.next/
dist/
tsconfig.tsbuildinfo

# --- Local DB / artifacts ---
*.db
*.db-shm
*.db-wal
*.duckdb

# --- VCS / tooling / docs ---
.git
.gitignore
*.log
README.md
